Photo, Bye-Bye Sheep -- After a San Pedro Municipal Court rejected his bid to 
keep eight sheep on acreage near an apartment complex he owns at Pacific Avenue 
and 24th Street, developer Arthur Corona held a roundup Wednesday to ship the 
flock to a farm in Chino. Perhaps best suited for the task at hand was the 
family dog. Corona, below left, also got some help from Samuel Rodriguez, in 
