COMPAGNONE / Los Angeles Times; Photo, A 1987 rehearsal of "I Don't Have to 
Show You No Stinkin' Badges." From left, Anne Betancourt, Leon Singer, Patti 
Yasutake, Tony Curiel and playwright Luis Valdez. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
