WEAPONS; WEAPONS SMUGGLING -- UNITED STATES; ARRESTS -- SAN DIEGO COUNTY; 
ARRESTS -- ORANGE COUNTY; DRUG ENFORCEMENT ADMINISTRATION; CUSTOMS SERVICE 
(U.S.) 
