POLICE HEADQUARTERS OPENS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Los Angeles Police Department has opened its new Southwest Division 
headquarters, a 22,000-square-foot facility in the Baldwin Hills Crenshaw Plaza 
shopping mall at Marlton Avenue and Martin Luther King Boulevard. 
</P>
<P>
