WILLIAM R; KIDNAPINGS -- LEBANON; EXECUTIONS -- LEBANON; MURDERS -- LEBANON; 
AMERICANS -- LEBANON; HOSTAGES -- LEBANON; TERRORISM -- LEBANON; THREATS; VIDEO 
RECORDINGS 
</P>
